{{Navlist/Top}}
The Advanced level of this book is for those familiar with the internal structure of the elements of language, who want to learn how to create sophisticated, unusual, and even really exotic conlangs. It aims to introduce you to language features and techniques that can be used to create conlangs with extra flair.
== What's in this level? ==
Each section describes features and techniques in a different aspect of language design. The sections are: *'''[[Conlang/Advanced/Sounds|Phonology]]''': Unusual ways to make speech sounds. *'''[[Conlang/Advanced/Grammar|Grammar]]''': Unusual ways to form and arrange words. *'''[[Conlang/Advanced/Language-Culture link|The link between a Language and its Culture]]'''. *'''[[Conlang/Advanced/Metaphor|Metaphor and its applications for Conlanging]]'''.
{{Navlist/Bottom}}

