{{ingredient}}
'''Onion powder''' is made from finely ground dehydrated [[Cookbook:Onion|onion]]s, mainly the pungent varieties of bulb onions, which causes the powder to have a very strong smell.
Onion powder comes in a few varieties: *White onion powder *Red onion powder *Yellow onion powder *Toasted onion powder
