[[:w:en:User:Sai2020]]

[[:w:te:User:Sai2020]]

A '''bend knot''' is a knot used to join two lengths of rope.

Although the [[Knots/Binding knots/Reef knot|Reef knot]] can be used in this way, it is insecure when used as a bend and so is not classed as one.

